+ ./cli
cli - Sample application

Usage:
  cli [OPTIONS] COMMAND
  cli [COMMAND] --help | -h
  cli --version | -v

Commands:
  admin          Admin operations

+ ./cli -h
cli - Sample application

Usage:
  cli [OPTIONS] COMMAND
  cli [COMMAND] --help | -h
  cli --version | -v

Commands:
  admin          Admin operations
  admin list     List connected devices

Global Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

+ ./cli admin -h
cli admin - Admin operations

Usage:
  cli admin COMMAND
  cli admin [COMMAND] --help | -h

