  list     List connected devices

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

+ export SHOW_PLEASE=1
+ SHOW_PLEASE=1
+ ./cli -h
cli - Sample application

Usage:
  cli [OPTIONS] COMMAND
  cli [COMMAND] --help | -h
  cli --version | -v

Commands:
  admin          Admin operations
  admin list     List connected devices
  admin reboot   Reboot

Global Options:
  --debug
    Enable debug mode

  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

Environment Variables:
  SECRET
    Set secret key

+ ./cli admin -h
cli admin - Admin operations

